           { emoji: "üåª", name: "Fatou S.", location: "Accra, Ghana ‚Ä¢ Age 55 ‚Ä¢ Post-menopause", quote: "As a grandmother, I want to prepare my daughters.‚ÄØDada gave me the language and knowledge to start these important conversations in our family.", tags: ["Family Conversations", "Intergenerational", "Education"] }
